{
  "texts": [
    "We introduce similar variables c ijkl for mappable edge pairs ij ∈ E 1 and kl ∈ E 2 with a(i) = a(j) and a(k) = a(l) with corresponding weights w ijkl = |bðijÞ À bðklÞ|.",
    "Finally, we have variables n ij for all ij ∈ E 1 ∪ E 2 to indicate whether an edge is not mapped.",
    "We denote by N(i) the neighborhood of node i, that is the set of adjacent nodes.",
    "Our ILP is as follows:",
    "y ik 2 f0, 1g for all mappable i 2 V 1 and k 2 V 2 ð9Þ c ijkl 2 f0, 1g for all mappable ij 2 E 1 and kl 2 E 2 ð10Þ"
  ]
}